channel.title: Silk Stalkings
channel.desc: Smut, smut and more smut - with sex and murder thrown in for good measure. Best friends Rita and Chris are a pair of homicide detectives who battle crime in the shadow of glitzy Palm Beach, Fla. As the series winds down, they are replaced by a former husband-and-wife team.

channel.title: Renegade
channel.desc: Framed for the murder of the woman he loved, ex-cop Reno Raines teams up with fellow bounty hunter Bobby Sixkiller to clear his name and avoid capture. And if he helps a gorgeous woman with a problem along the way, so much the better.
